headline: Tractor Supply (TSCO) Expands to 2,400 Stores Is Its Rural Footprint Strategy Nearing a Turning Point?
summary: Tractor Supply Company recently marked a milestone by opening its 2,400th store in Aiken, South Carolina, featuring a 3,000 square foot Garden Center and supporting the local equine community with a US$2,400 donation to Aiken Equine Rescue. This expansion, part of a broader plan to add about 100 new stores in 2026, comes as management highlights how mild winter weather may affect fourth-quarter results and emphasizes the importance of upcoming guidance for the year ahead. headline: Q3 Earnings Highs And Lows: Tractor Supply (NASDAQ:TSCO) Vs The Rest Of The Specialty Retail Stocks
summary: The end of an earnings season can be a great time to discover new stocks and assess how companies are handling the current business environment. Let’s take a look at how Tractor Supply (NASDAQ:TSCO) and the rest of the specialty retail stocks fared in Q3.
